title: Elton John: Still Standing | I'm Gonna Love Me Again | 4
description:
Elton’s finally getting his addictions under control. But just as he gets his life back on track, he suffers a series of devastating losses. After all these years, can Elton find a purpose in the pain, and carve out a little slice of happiness?
